I"~<p><img src="/assets/img/cpp/gtkmm-cpp.jpg" alt="Learn to Create a Graphical Application with C++ and GTKmm" /></p>

<p><a href="https://www.gtkmm.org/en/">Gtkmm</a> is the official C++ interface for the popular GTK GUI library. gtkmm is free software distributed under the GNU Lesser General Public License (LGPL).</p>

<p><a href="https://terminalroot.com.br/cpp">C++</a> is a compiled multi-paradigm programming language (its support includes imperative, object-oriented and generic language) and general use. Since the 1990s, it has been one of the most popular commercial languages, and is also widely used in academia for its great performance and user base. It was created by Bjarne Stroustrup.</p>

