<p>In this video we built the layout via code with the gtkmm library, a clone application of the old <a href="https://discourse.mozilla.org/t/password-exporter-https-addons-mozilla-org-en-us-firefox-addon-password-exporter/27052/6">Password Exporter</a>, an application for Firefox that has been discontinued, but we are going to recreate it as an exercise, however, by exporting the saved logins and passwords data in the browser with a file <a href="https://en.terminalroot.com.br/18-ways-to-generate-and-store-strong-passwords/">encrypted</a> with <a href="https://gnupg.org/">GNUPG</a> .</p>

