<h1 id="installation">Installation</h1>

<p>On <a href="https://en.terminalroot.com.br/10-fundamental-tips-for-your-gentoo-linux/">Gentoo</a>, Funtoo and similar</p>

<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">emerge gtkmm</code></pre></figure>

<p>In <a href="https://en.terminalroot.com.br/why-i-gave-up-on-debian/">Debian</a>, <a href="https://en.terminalroot.com.br/customize-your-ubuntu-with-wayland-sway-ulauncher-waybar/">Ubuntu</a>, <a href="https://en.terminalroot.com.br/transform-your-mint-ubuntu-or-debian-with-bspwm-polybar-rofi/">Linux Mint</a> and similar</p>

<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"><span class="nb">sudo </span>apt-get <span class="nb">install </span>libgtkmm-3.0-dev</code></pre></figure>

<p>And for Fedora, <a href="https://en.terminalroot.com.br/take-multiple-free-red-hat-linux-courses/">Red Hat</a> and the like</p>

<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"><span class="nb">sudo </span>dnf <span class="nb">install </span>gtkmm30-devel  </code></pre></figure>

